:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"Latest Easter Updates for UpdraftPlus and UpdraftCentral released\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/AvPaYOTA6ZE/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://updraftplus.com/latest-easter-updates-for-updraftplus-and-updraftcentral-released/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 24 Apr 2019 15:14:42 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"UpdraftCentral\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"UpdraftPlus development news\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=379873\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:854:\"<p>During the recent Easter holidays, the UpdraftPlus team have been working hard getting the latest updates out to our loyal customers. Our newest updates are for UpdraftPlus 1.16.12,UpdraftCentral 0.8.6 (Free) and UpdraftCentral 0.8.2 (Premium). The latest update for UpdraftPlus includes &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/latest-easter-updates-for-updraftplus-and-updraftcentral-released/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/latest-easter-updates-for-updraftplus-and-updraftcentral-released/\">Latest Easter Updates for UpdraftPlus and UpdraftCentral released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2788:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">During the recent Easter holidays, the UpdraftPlus team have been working hard getting the latest updates out to our loyal customers. Our newest updates are for UpdraftPlus 1.16.12,</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftCentral </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">0.8.6 (Free) and UpdraftCentral 0.8.2 (Premium).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The latest update for UpdraftPlus includes the fix of an regression issue which caused PcIZip unzips to run slow. Thanks to this fix, we are confident that your experience with UpdraftPlus will be better than ever before.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another new feature that we are excited to share is the new option that allows UpdraftCentral Premium users to suspend a site. There are numerous reasons that may require you to suspend a site; these can include the non-payment of hosting fees or even a violation of policies. With the latest UpdraftCentral update, you now have this option directly at your fingertips.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users.</span></p>\n<p><b>UpdraftPlus 1.16.12 </b></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIX: Regression which caused PclZip unzips to be very slow</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Add stream_meta to the list of log tables and tables not requiring search/replace</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><b>UpdraftCentral 0.8.6 (Free)</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>FIX: Fix fetching of updates fails if permissions fail on one site</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Add parameters to some filters</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Add specificity to some general CSS</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Update bundled UUDRPC library to version 1.4.18</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Backup status checks are now performed less often once a backup lasts longer than 3 minutes</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><b>UpdraftCentral 0.8.2 (Premium)</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> FEATURE: Add capability to suspend a site<br />\n</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/latest-easter-updates-for-updraftplus-and-updraftcentral-released/\">Latest Easter Updates for UpdraftPlus and UpdraftCentral released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://updraftplus.com/latest-easter-updates-for-updraftplus-and-updraftcentral-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://updraftplus.com/latest-easter-updates-for-updraftplus-and-updraftcentral-released/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"New and updated How to use site-to-site WordPress Migrator video released\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/mS2oqiqu9S0/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:106:\"https://updraftplus.com/new-and-updated-how-to-use-site-to-site-wordpress-migrator-video-released/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 17 Apr 2019 11:26:54 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Training materials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Clone Wordpress site\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Migrator\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Updraftplus migrator\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"WordPress Clone\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Migration\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WordPress migrator\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=377083\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:826:\"<p>UpdraftPlus Migrator is a powerful, easy to use and popular feature that enables users to clone or migrate a source WordPress site to a destination WordPress site in just a few minutes. We are pleased to announce that a new &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/new-and-updated-how-to-use-site-to-site-wordpress-migrator-video-released/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/new-and-updated-how-to-use-site-to-site-wordpress-migrator-video-released/\">New and updated &#8220;How to use site-to-site WordPress Migrator&#8221; video released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2179:\"<p><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/migrator/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus Migrator</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a powerful, easy to use and popular feature that enables users to clone or migrate a source WordPress site to a destination WordPress site in just a few minutes. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are pleased to announce that a new and updated UpdraftPlus Migrator how-to video guide has now been released. As this was the most requested video on our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/UpdraftPlus\">YouTube channel,</a> we are happy to provide Migrator users with a detailed guide to take you through the full process of migrating a WordPress site. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While there is an in-depth <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/faqs/how-do-i-migrate-to-a-new-site-location/\">written Migrator guide</a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, we know that many users prefer the visual and audio instructions that a video tutorial video provides. We always try to give as many different options for support and guidance as possible and hope that this new Migrator how-to video will be a useful helping-hand should you need any additional instruction.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Check out the video and be sure to let us know what you think in the comments section below; Also share with us any ideas you may have if you think there are any other how-to videos you would like to see.</span></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/330503168?dnt=1&#038;app_id=122963\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"How to use Direct Site-To-Site WordPress Migrator\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/new-and-updated-how-to-use-site-to-site-wordpress-migrator-video-released/\">New and updated &#8220;How to use site-to-site WordPress Migrator&#8221; video released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:103:\"https://updraftplus.com/new-and-updated-how-to-use-site-to-site-wordpress-migrator-video-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://updraftplus.com/new-and-updated-how-to-use-site-to-site-wordpress-migrator-video-released/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"WP-Optimize announce release of new leading image compression feature\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/9lFGz2047xg/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:102:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-announce-release-of-new-leading-image-compression-feature/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 12 Apr 2019 13:53:35 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP Optimize\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"image compression\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Smush\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Smushing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WP-Optimise Update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP-Optimize\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=374989\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:807:\"<p>As mentioned in our previous preview blog, we have been hard at work developing a new image compression tool for the latest WP-Optimize 2.3.0 (free + paid) release. Our image compression service is an easy to use and handy imaging &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-announce-release-of-new-leading-image-compression-feature/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-announce-release-of-new-leading-image-compression-feature/\">WP-Optimize announce release of new leading image compression feature</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4680:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As mentioned in our previous preview </span><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/smush-image-optimization/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">blog</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, we have been hard at work developing a new image compression tool for the latest WP-Optimize 2.3.0 (free + paid) release. Our image compression service is an easy to use and handy imaging tool that allows you to quickly and easily optimise, compress and resize images on your website.</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_375009\" style=\"width: 1869px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-375009\" class=\"wp-image-375009 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1859\" height=\"793\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33.jpg 1859w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33-300x128.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33-768x328.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33-1080x461.jpg 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-33-510x218.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1859px) 100vw, 1859px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-375009\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">How the image compression option will look in WP-Optimize</p></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As unnecessarily large website images can cause frustratingly slow website loading speeds, we identified the need for a new image compression tool within WP-Optimize. Large images can impact on a websites user experience, bounce rate and SEO performance, but with our new image compression options you can improve these factors without compromising quality. </span></p>\n<p><b>How Image Compression Works</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">By using the best-in-class Lossy and Lossless compression techniques; WP-Optimize can offer massive savings in image file size and saves the new compressed file in your image library. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have a lot of images on your website, you can also use our bulk editing option to compress as many images as you want at the same time &#8211; or even set-up &#8216;Auto-Compress&#8217;, which enables you to set WP-Optimize to automatically compress your images as and when they are uploaded. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In order to achieve big savings and increase speed, WP-Optimize gives you the option of choosing either Lossy or Lossless image compression. When using image compression methods, you may find that there may be a slight loss in image quality, but rest assured it will hardly even be noticeable. The Lossy compression method can achieve greater space savings when compared to Lossless, but Lossless compression allows you to keep file data and the original image quality.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For more information on the difference between Lossy and Lossless compression and what kind of results you can expect with WP-Optimize, be sure to check out our in-depth </span><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-image-compression-lossless-vs-lossy/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">recent blog</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> on this subject.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WP-Optimize doesnt limit you and will let you work with your favourite kind of images, allowing you to compress NG, JPG, GIF, BMP and TIF pictures up to 5mg in size. Our image optimisation service even allows you to backup your original files so you can quickly restore them in case you make a mistake or need the original full quality image.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also be assured that should you wish to remove the WP-Optimize plugin for whatever reason, your compressed images will remain unaffected, allowing you to keep all your new and original content and maintain full control over your website.</span></p>\n<p>Be sure to let us know any feedback comments you may have in the comment section below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-announce-release-of-new-leading-image-compression-feature/\">WP-Optimize announce release of new leading image compression feature</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-announce-release-of-new-leading-image-compression-feature/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-announce-release-of-new-leading-image-compression-feature/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:111:\"UpdraftPlus release latest update: Includes fixes for resuming an interrupted restore and Dropbox server issues\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/17rox6wskaY/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:144:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-latest-update-includes-fixes-for-resuming-an-interrupted-restore-and-dropbox-server-issues/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 10 Apr 2019 13:01:46 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"UpdraftPlus development news\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"UpdraftPlus development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"updraftplus premium\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"updraftplus update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=374117\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:956:\"<p>UpdraftPlus are happy to announce that we have released brand new updates for both the UpdraftPlus Free version (1.16.11) and UpdraftPlus Premium version (2.16.11). As part of our efforts to continually improve UpdraftPlus, we have fixed the option of the &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-latest-update-includes-fixes-for-resuming-an-interrupted-restore-and-dropbox-server-issues/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-latest-update-includes-fixes-for-resuming-an-interrupted-restore-and-dropbox-server-issues/\">UpdraftPlus release latest update: Includes fixes for resuming an interrupted restore and Dropbox server issues</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2846:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus are happy to announce that we have released brand new updates for both the UpdraftPlus Free version (1.16.11) and UpdraftPlus Premium version (2.16.11).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As part of our efforts to continually improve UpdraftPlus, we have fixed the option of the user being able to restore the update from a point of error that was encountered during the restoring process. Issues that could occur during a restore might include a restore time-out, loss of connection or an unintended error. This option saves users time as you will not have to restart the restore process from the beginning again should you encounter an issue. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another change we have made to the latest update includes a number of helpful tweaks to the Dropbox backup process. As users have had some issues with their servers using Dropbox, the update will hopefully help keep things running more smoothly and resolve these problems. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As well as this new feature, the latest update also come with several other fixes and tweaks to hopefully help improve your overall UpdraftPlus experience. .</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> FIX: Issue which prevented the downloader UI being removed during a manual entity download (regression)</span></li>\n<li>FIX: Regression in 1.16.10 whereby restore resumptions did not correctly resume because the jobdata had not been loaded</li>\n<li>TWEAK: Update UpdraftCentral description and internationalize strings</li>\n<li>TWEAK: Handle HTTP/2 responses from Dropbox on some operations</li>\n<li>TWEAK: Add a timeout on Dropbox quota look-up operations during backup, in response to cases of faulty outgoing HTTP proxies</li>\n<li>TWEAK: The backup_finish() method should not have been private; could cause a harmless PHP abort when manually stopping a backup</li>\n<li>TWEAK: Wrong variable context could cause failure of SFTP progress recording</li>\n<li>TWEAK: Update to the current series (4.6) of yahnis-elsts/plugin-update-checker (paid versions), thereby inheriting improvements including suppressing some unnecessary background updates checks&#8220;`</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-latest-update-includes-fixes-for-resuming-an-interrupted-restore-and-dropbox-server-issues/\">UpdraftPlus release latest update: Includes fixes for resuming an interrupted restore and Dropbox server issues</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:140:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-latest-update-includes-fixes-for-resuming-an-interrupted-restore-and-dropbox-server-issues/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:135:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-latest-update-includes-fixes-for-resuming-an-interrupted-restore-and-dropbox-server-issues/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"Lossy vs Lossless image compression  A guide to the trade-off between image size and quality\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/G3y7XOOrLt4/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-image-compression-lossless-vs-lossy/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 09 Apr 2019 09:39:29 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:9:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP Optimize\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"image comprression\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"lossless and lossy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Smushing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"WP-O\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP-Optimise\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WP-Optimise Update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP-Optimize\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WP-Optmize update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=360303\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:817:\"<p>With the launch of WP-Optimizes new smushing image compression feature, many people may be unaware of the advantages and disadvantages of the Lossy and Lossless compression methods. This blog will explain in detail what kind of results and savings you &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-image-compression-lossless-vs-lossy/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-image-compression-lossless-vs-lossy/\">Lossy vs Lossless image compression &#8211; A guide to the trade-off between image size and quality</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12141:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With the launch of WP-Optimizes new smushing image compression feature, many people may be unaware of the advantages and disadvantages of the Lossy and Lossless compression methods. This blog will explain in detail what kind of results and savings you can expect to achieve with each compression format.</span></p>\n<h3><b>Lossy Compression</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-370247\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"483\" height=\"246\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy.jpg 483w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy-300x153.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 483px) 100vw, 483px\" /></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The most popular image compression for most users is Lossy, which can be categorized as achieving greater space saving compression (compared to Lossless), but losses some of the data and image quality from the original image in the compression process. While you can save more data with Lossy, the data saving isn&#8217;t completely without cost, as with increased compression comes a slight increased degradation in the image quality and the inability to you reverse the compression, which results in the permanent loss of file metadata. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You should choose the Lossy method of compression If you are purely trying to reduce the size of your images and save data. But remember that the advantage of smaller files will be tempered by the small reduction in quality in your images and the permanent loss of metadata.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This isnt to say that your new compressed image will resemble a digital camera photo from 2002 however. The image will still be very high quality and present as a professional and clear image, but you may start to get some compression artifacts appear with high levels of compression.</span></p>\n<p>With Lossy compression enabled, the below image was compressed from <strong>230.26 KB to 64.92 KB, giving an almost 75% reduction in size.</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_373540\" style=\"width: 608px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373540\" class=\"wp-image-373540 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original.jpg 598w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original-300x200.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original-510x339.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-373540\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Original JPEG image</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_373548\" style=\"width: 608px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy-2.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373548\" class=\"wp-image-373548 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy-2.jpg 598w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy-2-510x339.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-373548\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">How image looks converted with Lossy compression</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_373543\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a style=\"font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original300.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373543\" class=\"wp-image-373543 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original300.jpg 690w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original300-300x228.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original300-510x388.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-373543\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Original image zoomed in 300%</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_373544\" style=\"width: 703px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a style=\"font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy300.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373544\" class=\"wp-image-373544 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"693\" height=\"528\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy300.jpg 693w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy300-300x229.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossy300-510x389.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 693px) 100vw, 693px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-373544\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lossy image zoomed in 300% &#8211; 230.26 KB to 64.92 KB, a 75% reduction in size</p></div>\n<p><b>Lossy Summary</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pro &#8211; Can reduce the images to small sizes and save lots of file data, making your website load quicker and perform better.<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Con &#8211; The smaller you make the file size, the lower the quality of your original image. Deletes original image data permanently.</span></p>\n<h3><b>Lossless Compression</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-370246\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"203\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless.jpg 437w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\" /></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lossless is a term that refers to a class of data compression algorithms that compresses your image, but allows the original data to be restored and reconstructed from the compressed file</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> data should you ever need it.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Lossless compression differs to Lossy by maintaining the original image quality, while reducing the image data size by removing unnecessary meta-data from the submitted files (usually JPEG or PNG files). The main benefit of this type of compression is that the user has the ability to keep all the original data and revert to the original image, but can still achieve a smaller file size, without sacrificing image quality. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As previously mentioned, one of the main benefits of Lossless compression is being able to keep and restore every single bit of data that was within the file after it is uncompressed. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This is in contrast to Lossy compression, where metadata is not saved during the compression process and results in data being unable to be restored should you wish to reverse the compression.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a Lossless image will only temporarily delete the file data, this allows it to be transferred quicker, which results in faster loading speeds for your website. While the amount of space you will save is not as much as if you were to use Lossy compression, it does give you higher quality images and the option to fully restore should you need it.</span></p>\n<p>With Lossless compression enabled, the below image was compressed from <strong>230.26 KB to 172.18 KB, giving just over 25% reduction in size.</strong></p>\n<div style=\"width: 608px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"398\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Original JPEG image</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_373542\" style=\"width: 608px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless-1.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373542\" class=\"wp-image-373542 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless-1.jpg 598w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless-1-510x339.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-373542\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Converted with Lossless compression. Every pixel is identical to the original image &#8211; only the file size is smaller</p></div>\n<div style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Original300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"525\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Original image zoomed in 300%</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_373541\" style=\"width: 706px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless300.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373541\" class=\"wp-image-373541 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"696\" height=\"519\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless300.jpg 696w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless300-300x224.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Lossless300-510x380.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-373541\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lossless image zoomed in 300% &#8211; 230.26 KB to 172.18 KB, a 25% reduction in size</p></div>\n<p><b>LosslessSummary</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pro &#8211; Decreases image file size but maintains original quality of image. Full restoration of data available.<br />\n</span>Con &#8211; Using Lossless compression results in larger files sizes in comparison to Lossy compression, which can result in slower loading speeds.</p>\n<h3><strong>Custom</strong></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Custom.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-370249\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Custom.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"203\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Custom.jpg 437w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Custom-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We understand that some users may wish to decide their own balance between maximum compression and best image quality. With the custom option, you can manually choose which settings your prefer for image compression and save them for future use.</p>\n<p><b>Overall Compression Summary</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Making a choice between Lossless or Lossy compression depends on what you want to achieve and what works best for your site and users. In general terms, if you have a website that needs to showcase high quality photographs (such as a wedding photography business), you should stick to Lossless compression as it will still display your images in their original highest quality. But if your site is for a local garage for example, where the highest quality images are not so important, Lossy compression could work best as original high quality photos are not essential to the success of your business. </span></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-image-compression-lossless-vs-lossy/\">Lossy vs Lossless image compression &#8211; A guide to the trade-off between image size and quality</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-image-compression-lossless-vs-lossy/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-image-compression-lossless-vs-lossy/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"New How to use incremental backups video released\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/BYVpk-pE8VE/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-launch-new-how-to-use-incremental-backups-video/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 28 Mar 2019 14:23:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Training materials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"automatic backups\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"incremental backups\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"UpdraftPlus development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"updraftplus premium\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=368744\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:823:\"<p>If you are thinking of backing up your WordPress site content, such as images, media, video, plugins and themes by using UpdraftPlus&#8217; incremental backup feature, you may be interested in our new &#8216;How to use incremental backups&#8217; instructional video. While &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-launch-new-how-to-use-incremental-backups-video/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-launch-new-how-to-use-incremental-backups-video/\">New &#8216;How to use incremental backups&#8217; video released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1670:\"<p>If you are thinking of backing up your WordPress site content, such as images, media, video, plugins and themes by using UpdraftPlus&#8217; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-launch-revoluntionary-new-incremental-backups-feature/\">incremental backup</a> feature, you may be interested in our new &#8216;How to use incremental backups&#8217; instructional video.</p>\n<p>While we have existing in-depth <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/how-to-use-incremental-backups/\">written instructions</a> on how to use incremental backups, we understand that some people may prefer the quick, visual method of learning and instruction that a video gives. We are always happy to provide our users with different options and hope that the new instructional video provides additional support.</p>\n<p>The video goes through the process of showing you how to take a one-off incremental backup and also how to schedule and setup your incremental backups.</p>\n<p>Check out the video below and be sure to let us know what you think in the comment section.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/326843484?dnt=1&#038;app_id=122963\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"How to use Incremental Backups\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-launch-new-how-to-use-incremental-backups-video/\">New &#8216;How to use incremental backups&#8217; video released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-launch-new-how-to-use-incremental-backups-video/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-launch-new-how-to-use-incremental-backups-video/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"UpdraftPlus latest release now includes support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/LxvRGM10paQ/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:122:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 25 Mar 2019 10:23:19 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"UpdraftPlus development news\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"updraft plus development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"UpdraftPlus\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"updraftplus update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=367357\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:862:\"<p>UpdraftPlus are happy to announce that we have been hard at work on a new update that we are now happy to share with you. The latest update of UpdraftPlus 1.16.10 includes several additional fixes and tweaks, including an all &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\">UpdraftPlus latest release now includes support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3421:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus are happy to announce that we have been hard at work on a new update that we are now happy to share with you. The latest update of UpdraftPlus 1.16.10 includes several additional fixes and tweaks, including an all new feature that gives support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Structured Query Language (SQL) is a standard computer language that is used for relational database management and data manipulation. SQL users typically use it to query, insert, update and modify data. Developing specific triggers that meet your SQL requirements can be a long term project with in depth processes that are unique to your specific database queries and requirements. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With UpdraftPlus 1.16.10, you will never have to worry about losing your valuable SQL triggers again should you suffer an issue with your site, such as a virus or a malicious hack. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So from now on, when you are using SQL to perform tasks such as update, analyse or retrieve data from your database, you can be assured that should the worst happen UpdraftPlus will allow you to restore the SQL triggers that you have developed, saving your valuable data, time and effort. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As well as this new feature, UpdraftPlus 1.16.10 also come with several other fixes and tweaks to make your UpdraftPlus experience even better. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We hope this new update will help improve your experience when using UpdraftPlus</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users. </span></p>\n<h4><b>UpdraftPlus 1.16.10</b></h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FEATURE: Added support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIX: Prevent the downloader UI being removed before its complete in the case of multi-archive sets (regression)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Refactor the restore code and use jobdata to save information about the restore rather than using $_POST data</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Automatically show the UpdraftClone admin UI for UpdraftClone developers for easier debugging</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Prevent a PHP notice with certain exclusion settings</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Add a mention of UpdraftClone in WPs PHP version notice and WooCommerces untested extensions notice</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Add 5.1 to the built-in list of available UpdraftClone WP versions</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\">UpdraftPlus latest release now includes support for backing up and restoring SQL triggers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:119:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:114:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-latest-release-now-includes-support-for-backing-up-and-restoring-sql-triggers/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"Access and upload images directly from Unsplash.com with the latest MetaSlider update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/yVIVBo5lZgg/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:118:\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 22 Mar 2019 09:44:41 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"MetaSlider\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"MetaSlider themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"MetaSlider update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=366353\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:858:\"<p>We are excited to announce that MetaSlider users now have the option of using the all new Unsplash.com library feature. When creating a new slideshow in MetaSlider, you now have the option to search and add images from a Unsplash.com &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\">Access and upload images directly from Unsplash.com with the latest MetaSlider update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7461:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are excited to announce that MetaSlider users now have the option of using the all new Unsplash.com library feature. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When creating a new slideshow in MetaSlider, you now have the option to search and add images from a Unsplash.com tab that behaves just like your very own personal massive media library. This incredibly handy new feature means there is no need to leave your WordPress page to search for images, and then try to remember where they are saved when adding them to your slideshow.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With our new feature, the search and upload of images with Upsplash.com can now all be done from within the MetaSlider plugin. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upsplash.com has over 850,000 completely free to use (do whatever you want with them) high-resolution photos that have been contributed by a large community of photographers from all over the world. Thousands of additional photos are added every day, with the types of images available covering a huge amount of topics and themes. With so much choice there is a very good chance that Upsplash.com has the type of photos you are looking for. </span></p>\n<p><b>How to use the new Upsplash.com feature in MetaSlider</b></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366366\" style=\"width: 792px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366366\" class=\"wp-image-366366\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"782\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8.jpg 1351w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-300x95.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-768x243.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-1024x324.jpg 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-1080x341.jpg 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-8-510x161.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 782px) 100vw, 782px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366366\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Just select Add Slide and click on the Unsplash Library tab.</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366365\" style=\"width: 766px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a style=\"font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366365\" class=\"wp-image-366365 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"756\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9.jpg 756w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9-300x107.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-9-510x182.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 756px) 100vw, 756px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366365\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Use the Search unsplash.com search option to find the images you want.</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366364\" style=\"width: 523px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366364\" class=\"wp-image-366364 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"513\" height=\"725\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10.jpg 513w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10-212x300.jpg 212w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-10-510x721.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366364\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Select your favourite and click Add to slideshow&#8221;.</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366362\" style=\"width: 1146px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366362\" class=\"wp-image-366362\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1136\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12.jpg 1551w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-300x132.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-768x337.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-1024x450.jpg 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-1080x474.jpg 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-12-510x224.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1136px) 100vw, 1136px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366362\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Unsplash.com image you added automatically uploads to your library and is added to your new slideshow. It really is that easy!</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366361\" style=\"width: 983px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366361\" class=\"wp-image-366361 size-full\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"973\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13.jpg 973w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13-300x131.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13-768x335.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-Project-13-510x223.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 973px) 100vw, 973px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-366361\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Slideshow preview</p></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br />\nMetaSlider is available for download </span><a href=\"https://metaslider.com/upgrade/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">here</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Sign up and download it to your WordPress website today and let the fun begin. If you have any comments about the latest update, be sure to let us know in the comments below.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users:</span></p>\n<p><b>Change log</b></p>\n<p><b>3.12.0  2019/MAR/18</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Sets a default theme on a newly created slideshow</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">TWEAK: Adds various trivial code quality fixes</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIX: Fixes a bug where Nivo and Coin Slider did not ship with the plugin</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FEATURE: Adds access to the Unsplash.com image library</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\">Access and upload images directly from Unsplash.com with the latest MetaSlider update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:115:\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:110:\"https://updraftplus.com/access-and-upload-images-directly-from-unsplash-com-with-the-latest-metaslider-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"UpdraftPlus release new 1.16.8 update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/VBNX1DYUTbE/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 14 Mar 2019 10:30:07 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"UpdraftPlus development news\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"UpdraftClone\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"UpdraftPlus development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"updraftplus update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=363079\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:710:\"<p>UpdraftPlus are pleased to announce that we have released a new update: UpdraftPlus 1.16.8. We have been hard at work on the latest developments, with our main aim being to fix the issue of a potential rapidly repeating loop that &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/\">UpdraftPlus release new 1.16.8 update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1310:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus are pleased to announce that we have released a new update: UpdraftPlus 1.16.8. We have been hard at work on the latest developments, with our main aim being to fix the issue of a potential rapidly repeating loop that could occur if requested </span><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftClone</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> credentials were not ready.</span></p>\n<p>We hope this new update help improve your experience when using UpdraftPlus.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIX: If requesting clone credentials that were not ready, the loop could rapidly repeat instead of waiting the intended time</span></li>\n<li>TWEAK: Some background updates checks (paid versions) that were intended to be suppressed, weren&#8217;t being.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/\">UpdraftPlus release new 1.16.8 update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"WP-Optimize 2.2.13 new update released\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/GU984mPsBvQ/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-13-now-released/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 13 Mar 2019 11:48:46 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP Optimize\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"WP-O\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP-Optimise\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WP-Optimise Update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"WP-Optimize\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WP-Optmize update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=362619\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:706:\"<p>We are pleased to announce that we have released an updated version of WP-Optimize 2.2.13 for both free and paid versions. The latest update includes a few fixes and tweaks that we hope will make your WP-Optimize experience even better. &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-13-now-released/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-13-now-released/\">WP-Optimize 2.2.13 new update released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:988:\"<p>We are pleased to announce that we have released an updated version of WP-Optimize 2.2.13 for both free and paid versions.</p>\n<p>The latest update includes a few fixes and tweaks that we hope will make your WP-Optimize experience even better.</p>\n<p>We recommend the update for all WP-Optimize users.</p>\n<p>The full changelog is as follows;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>FIX: Fixed RTL layout</li>\n<li>FIX: Detect more relationships between tables and plugins in orphaned database tables optimization</li>\n<li>FIX: Fixed orphaned relationships optimization</li>\n<li>TWEAK: The informational list of WP core tables missed some possible extra tables on multisite</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-13-now-released/\">WP-Optimize 2.2.13 new update released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-13-now-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-13-now-released/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:39:\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/UpdraftPlus\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"rel\";s:3:\"hub\";s:4:\"href\";s:32:\"http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:4:\"info\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"uri\";s:11:\"updraftplus\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_la