(274, 2, '2019-04-25 05:04:58', '2019-04-25 05:04:58', '', 'The grandest festival in Zamboanga is already a few months away! Zamboanga Hermosa Festival, also known as Fiesta Pilar, is one of the oldest and most colorful festivals in the country. The festival is held every October in honor of the city\'s patroness, Nuestra Seora La Virgen del Pilar.', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-grandest-festival-in-zamboanga-is-already-a-few-months-away-zamboanga-hermosa-festival-also-known-as-fiesta-pilar-is-one-of-the-oldest-and-most-colorful-festivals-in-the-country-the-festi__trashed', '', '', '2019-04-25 05:06:36', '2019-04-25 05:06:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/zamboangacity.gov.ph/?post_type=slider-image&#038;p=274', 0, 'slider-image', '', 0),
